{"tid":2239653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（痴撚線）中國8.5萬人確診列「防疫成功國家第一」　台灣未進榜！","createTime":"2020-10-12T06:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:24:24.000Z","uid":66087,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec9f24d2b915ef1e4f0faf967d7f188b1476595","tid":2239653,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"記者林彥臣／台北綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n全球衛生研究所（ISGlobal）與紐約城市大學公衛研究院（CUNY SPH）針對新冠肺炎（COVID-19）防疫最成功國家進行排名，官方公布數據8.5萬人確診、4634人死亡，並且在武漢實施76天封城措施的中國，以平均得分80.48分，在19個疫情最嚴重國家當中排名第一，至今累積523例確診，7人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（地圖）世界各國防疫措施總評分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWxkMxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWxkMxW.jpg&h=d0e1f4ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從未實施過封城的台灣，因為不在首批名單內，所以尚未進榜。<br />\n<br />\n根據紐約城市大學公衛研究院發布新聞稿指出，這項調查與全球衛生研究所合作，開發出一種簡單可靠的工具，可以評估世界民眾對於政府防疫措施的看法，並追蹤疫情發展趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報告原文：<a href=\"https://sph.cuny.edu/2020/10/06/covid-score/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsph.cuny.edu%2F2020%2F10%2F06%2Fcovid-score%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=5f292df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sph.cuny.edu/2020/10/06/covid-score/</a>"},{"pid":"cb02a66d9dc9dd2b43286f9b8b0e0891ec0b8e94","tid":2239653,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人查下呢間紐約城市大學乜料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d3fad93feba507850dd5566d10adb9e8f1e6a6","tid":2239653,"uid":239696,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"金正恩笑而不語"},{"pid":"2bec7aaf8b11c6ca1881af9228871023926ae628","tid":2239653,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"fake<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f32cbf71c1e53f0d32386aa45417b1499a6a69","tid":2239653,"uid":158270,"like":0,